    },
    {
        "Emergency Alert System": "Emergency Alert System"
    },
    {
        ".     The reference  Nuclear War Survival Skills  includes the following supplies in a list of Minimum Pre-Crisis Preparations : one or more shovels, a pick, a bow-saw with an extra blade, a hammer, and 4-mil polyethylene film ; a homemade shelter-ventilating pump ; large containers for water; a plastic bottle of sodium hypochlorite bleach; one or two ": null
