        ".        Inhabitants should plan to remain sheltered for at least two weeks , then work outside for gradually increasing amounts of time, to four hours a day at three weeks. The normal work is to sweep or wash fallout into shallow trenches to decontaminate the area. They should sleep in a shelter for several months. Evacuation at three weeks is recommended by official authorities.     If available, inhabitants may take ": null
